{"tid":1720079,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"宵禁喎","createTime":"2019-11-14T08:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T09:32:04.000Z","uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"86ea9c3694cbf2a6ec2b923e0e12322a55fd3cfc","tid":1720079,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492136-20191114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492136-20191114.htm&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVc85qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=97354dab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492136-20191114.htm&h=7c4d2c3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492136-20191114.htm</a><br />\n有傳政府高官昨晚開會，可能討論是否宵禁。法律界立法會議員郭榮鏗表示，要平息民憤及危機，不可以再透過強硬法例或增加警力處理，否則會激起更多民憤，做不到政府所講的止暴制亂。<br />\n<br />\n他說，如果要實施宵禁，最有可能根據公安條例進行，牽涉到公安條例能否符合人權法和基本法對人權的保障，如果根據緊急法宣布宵禁，將會嚴重打擊香港作為金融中心的地位。<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗認為，不應該引用緊急法取消區議會選舉，形容取消選舉會非常嚴重地傷害參選權及投票權，一旦取消會成為國際關注香港的原因。"},{"pid":"82b1d1a52ab0f5ae5cafd1838bf82323ac56c3b2","tid":1720079,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快少少啦"},{"pid":"9e97dfab4e4d83e8ce95dccc75a247687f2cea8e","tid":1720079,"uid":288304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86ea9c3694cbf2a6ec2b923e0e12322a55fd3cfc","tid":1720079,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492136-20191114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492136-20191114.htm&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVc85qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=97354dab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=ht